<Line lineWidth="90%" lineColor="var(--custom_black)" />
<section id="festivals">
  <h2>FESTIVALS</h2>
  <p>
    Svendborg, a coastal town in Denmark, hosts a vibrant array of festivals celebrating music, culture, sport, and food. The Sound Festival enchants music enthusiasts with diverse genres and
    captivating performances. Svendborg Arts Week immerses the town in creativity, showcasing artwork and performances that inspire dialogue. The Sports Festival offers thrilling competitions,
    fostering camaraderie among athletes and spectators.
  </p>
  <img src="../images/festival.jpg" alt="" />
  <p>
    The Food and Wine Festival indulges taste buds with a delectable array of flavors and aromas. Svendborg's festivals merge music, culture, sport, and food to create an unforgettable experience.
    From melodic concerts to artistic showcases, athletic competitions to culinary delights, the town's festivals have something for everyone. Immerse yourself in Svendborg's vibrant celebrations and
    discover the magic they offer.
  </p>
  <h3>Read more about festivals in Svendborg and dates here</h3>
  <a href="https://www.visitsvendborg.dk/svendborg/festivaler-i-svendborg">READ MORE</a>
</section>
<Line lineWidth="90%" lineColor="var(--custom_black)" />
<section id="activities">
  <h2>ACTIVITIES</h2>
  <p>
    If you are looking for an active holiday, Svendborg is the perfect starting point. Svendborg's breathtaking coastline invites adventure seekers to explore its waters through kayaking,
    paddleboarding, and sailing, offering a thrilling blend of sport and natural beauty.
  </p>
  <img src="../images/active.jpg" alt="" />
  <p>
    Hiking and biking trails weave through Svendborg's lush forests and picturesque landscapes, providing opportunities for outdoor enthusiasts to immerse themselves in nature.Svendborg's favorable
    wind conditions make it a haven for wind and kite surfers, who can take advantage of the open waters and exhilarating waves.
  </p>
</section>
<Line lineWidth="90%" lineColor="var(--custom_black)" />
<section id="nature">
  <h2>NATURE</h2>
  <p>
    With its diverse natural offerings, Svendborg captivates visitors with its coastal beauty, verdant forests, picturesque islands, and serene parks, making it an ideal destination for those seeking
    a connection with nature. Nestled on the coast, Svendborg offers breathtaking views of the sea, with tranquil beaches perfect for sunbathing, picnicking, and leisurely walks along the shoreline.
  </p>
  <p>The town is surrounded by lush forests and rolling hills, providing numerous hiking and biking trails that showcase the area's natural beauty, allowing visitors to explore at their own pace.</p>
  <div>
    <img src="../images/island.jpg" alt="image of Svendborg islands" />
    <img src="../images/nature.jpg" alt="" />
  </div>

  <p>
    Fishing enthusiasts can cast their lines into Svendborg's coastal waters, angling for a variety of fish species while enjoying the serenity of the surroundings.Yoga and meditation enthusiasts can
    partake in outdoor sessions, breathing in the fresh coastal air and finding tranquility amidst Svendborg's natural landscapes.
  </p>
  <p>
    Svendborg's fusion of nature and sport provides a wealth of active activities, ensuring that visitors can immerse themselves in the great outdoors while engaging in thrilling sports and
    recreational pursuits.
  </p>
</section>
<Line lineWidth="90%" lineColor="var(--custom_black)" />
<section id="music">
  <h2>ART & MUSIC</h2>
  <p>
    Svendborg offers a rich tapestry of cultural, artistic, and musical experiences that captivate visitors from near and far. Svendborg's historic landmarks, such as the iconic Svendborg Theatre,
    provide a backdrop for captivating theatrical performances, including plays, musicals, and ballet, enriching the cultural fabric of the town.
  </p>
  <img src="../images/music.jpg" alt="" />
  <p>
    The town's charming streets often come alive with buskers and street performers, adding a touch of spontaneous artistry and creating an immersive and interactive cultural experience for passersby.
    Harders Music, located in Svendborg, Denmark, is a renowned hub for music enthusiasts, offering a wide range of instruments, equipment, and expert advice, catering to both beginners and seasoned
    musicians. <br />
    <br />With its exceptional selection and knowledgeable staff, Harders Music is the go-to destination for all things music in Svendborg.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-block: 2rem;
  }
  /* HEADINGS  */
  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 7vw, 2rem);
    padding-block: 1rem;
  }
  h3 {
    text-align: center;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  /*  BODY TEXT */
  p {
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 2rem;
    padding-inline: 1rem;
  }
  /* IMAGES */
  img {
    object-fit: cover;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 400px;
  }
  /* LINKS */
  a {
    outline: 5px double var(--custom_black);
    color: var(--custom_black);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    padding: 0.5em;
  }
  section:first-of-type div {
    position: relative;
  }
  section:first-of-type div > a {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-50%);
    background-color: #354c8299;
    backdrop-filter: blur(1px);
    width: max-content;
    color: var(--custom_white);
    outline: 5px double var(--custom_white);
  }
  /* GENERAL LAYOUT */
  div {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  section:nth-of-type(4) img {
    object-position: bottom;
  }
  section:nth-of-type(4) div {
    width: 100%;
  }

  @media (min-width: 800px) {
    section {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      padding-block: 3rem;
      padding-inline: 2rem;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin:auto;
    }
    img {
      grid-row: span 2;
      max-width: 75ch;
      min-width: 80%;
    }
    h2 {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
    /* festivals section */
    section:nth-of-type(2) a,
    section:nth-of-type(2) h3 {
      grid-column: span 2;
      padding-block: 1rem;
    }
    section:nth-of-type(2) img {
      grid-row: 2/4;
      grid-column: 1/2;
      object-position: 0 -200px;
    }
    section:nth-of-type(2) p {
      grid-column: 2/3;
    }
    /* festivals section */
    section:nth-of-type(4) div {
      grid-row: 2/6;
      grid-column: 1/2;
      max-width: 75ch;
      max-height: 100%;
    }
    section:nth-of-type(4) img {
      max-height: 300px;
    }
  }
  @media (min-width: 1200px) {
  }
</style>
